Quickstrike:





"No," Quickstrike said flatly to Dark Mouse. He kept in his position. 
"Lisen, ah's gots lots t' do. And goin' on uh reckon ain't on mah things 
t'do! Tell Megtron ah ain't got th' time. Ah'm still waitin' fer that pod. 
Tarnation, ah'll tell 'im!" He turned his head to Black Arachnia. "Looks 
like we's have t' do this some other time." He walked off, towards 
Megatron's position.
